    "Similarly, upon integrating the CAF module into the model, we observed a notable improvement in the segmentation results.",
    "The CAF module effectively enhanced the feature fusion process with a 1.48% increase in the DC, allowing for better integration of complementary information from the efficientNetV2 and ViTs encoders.",
    "We noticed a similar increase in performance when training and testing on the BUSI dataset as well as when training on the BUSI dataset and testing on the UDIAT dataset.",
    "This improved feature fusion led to more precise and detailed segmentation boundaries, resulting in enhanced segmentation accuracy and overall performance.",
    "The ablation study results demonstrate the significant benefit of incorporating the CAF module, highlighting its effectiveness in improving the segmentation capabilities of our multitask framework.We compared the segmentation results with existing methods."
